Description:
Spin and attack all nearby foes in a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;2.5m&lt;/font&gt; radius, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[0.500000 * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage. You can move while spinning. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max 4 spins.) (This attack cannot backstab.)&lt;/font&gt;

&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;Whirlwind can be block/dodge cancelled after the first spin.&lt;/font&gt;

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

An upward swing dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[0.250000 * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and projecting a powerful tear in reality that creates a vortex up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[10.000000]}m&lt;/font&gt; away. The vortex pulls foes within &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[4.000000]}m&lt;/font&gt; to its center and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;roots&lt;/font&gt; them for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[1.000000]}s&lt;/font&gt;.

Foes within the vortex have their movement speed reduced by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[-0.600000 * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; due to the intense gravity.

The collapsing vortex ends after &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;3s&lt;/font&gt; with a damaging burst dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#edc63e"&gt;{[1.000000 * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_void_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;
